data.description: Amazing 4-5 bedroom 3.5BA Lake Arrowhead Home with spectacular views of the lake. Resort living with swim, tennis, lake use, and boat rentals right in your own neighborhood. This home is close to the back gate with easy access to Waleska and Canton. Main level features a gourmet kitchen with built-ins, solid surface countertops, family room, breakfast area, and sunroom.
data.whatILove: Added luxurious half bath, screened in porch on terrace level, landscaping and hardscaping.
